reviewText:
So sad to give this one star..

The original 1993 Les Visiteurs is one of my favorite movies of all times. The sequel was bad, this one is as bad as the sequel. I just love Clavier and Reno, yet this is such a weak movie.
I really loved this one. It's really different than the first and sequel, that's why I like it. Christian Clavier is amazing as always, Jean Reno is tired but still great.
HORRIBLE!  Do NOT buy this movie.  It's not funny like the previous ones.
